Text: Jurisprudence Luncheon Cc Jim It was an honor and a pleasure to meet both of you yesterday I know we will have fun working together on this very special event Jeff left the jurisprudence luncheon lists for me before he left on vacation I wasnt sure whether he transmitted them to you as well Would you please advise me if you would like them sent to you I can email the MS Excel files or I can fax the hard copies to you Please advise what is most convenient I plan to be in town through the holidays and can be reached by phone email or cell phone at any time My cell phone number is Thanks again for your interest in the ADLs work Martin Martin B Cominsky Director Southwest Region AntiDefamation League ext fax
